title: Lauren Tarshis - (Books 1-9) I Survived series [Epub & Mobi]
description:
Lauren Tarshis - (Books 1-9) I Survived series



The most terrifying events in history are brought vividly to life in this new fictional series!

The Sinking of the Titanic, 1912; I Survived the Shark Attacks of 1916; I Survived Hurricane Katrina, 2005; I Survived the Bombing of Pearl Harbor, 1941; I Survived the San Francisco Earthquake, 1906; I Survived the Attacks of September 11th, 2001; I Survived the Battle of Gettysburg, 1863; I Survived The Japanese Tsunami, 2011; The Nazi Invasion, 1944

Genre: Historical Fiction | Childrens
